Quote and Order Capture includes a new metadata type to create a contract from quote record.

New Metadata Type in Quote and Order Capture:
Create a contract from a quote record
Use the createContract value in the existing actionType field, which is on the FlowActionCall subtype on the Flow metadata type. Introduced in API version 60.0.
